{"tid":179783,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"自己行一次街就知呢個城市既人係幾不近人情","createTime":"2017-03-30T12:56:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-30T14:33:26.000Z","uid":26610,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"42a6660c6fd9658aacaeb96155f7b8ec812c63f8","tid":179783,"uid":26610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T12:56:02.000Z","msg":"我有個習慣每晚七點鐘都會迫自己四圍行幾個鐘唔留係屋企<br />\n所以基本上晚晚都係自己毒撚一個四圍鳩遊<br />\n話說今日出門比較匆忙 求其執套衫就出門口<br />\n依舊冇目的地咁行 都行左成幾k路 擦肩而過既路人不少<br />\n重點黎喇 行左個半鐘頭急尿 去左個公園廁所<br />\n唔去尤自可 一去把幾把火<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母原來我行撚左個半鐘一直冇拉褲鍊啊屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到底一撻地方既人要幾冷漠先會見到都唔提路人拉褲鏈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3a0962e1762f1d50563f63683c0afc00d29bc12","tid":179783,"uid":1567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T12:56:52.000Z","msg":"此post已完"},{"pid":"b8ea18cf91b93d892e874f23b3968fec5dc1f1f7","tid":179783,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T12:57:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9a4854b9aa63105cbaaf50a21c9b40b2b2251938","tid":179783,"uid":64178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T13:13:03.000Z","msg":"屌 <br />\n好撚認真咁睇<br />\n點知係咁撚樣"},{"pid":"a62e13c4fe332887d0ea1990f501a3027757755a","tid":179783,"uid":3571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T13:15:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"080b9475998a64eaf931fb579e3e4c738b65415b","tid":179783,"uid":3571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T13:15:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"p